casebody.data:
No. 135,

October term, 1914.

Wilson Cypress Company, Appellant, v. Enrique del Pozo y Marcos et al. Submitted April 24, 1916. Decided May 1, 1916. Mr. William W. Dewhurst, Mr. Joseph H. Jones, and Mr. John C. Jones for the petitioners. Mr. John C. Cooper in opposition thereto.

Motion for leave to file in the trial court a supplemental bill in the nature of a bill of review denied.
